* Design *                 -*-muse-*-

 * Mental model first
 * Simplify before coding
 * Fundamental data types
 * Fundamental operations
 * Use cases
 * Core/added functions
 * Short files (200 lines)
 * Short functions (5 lines)
 * Small modules (10 files)
 * Constant refactoring
 * Do one thing (module, class, function)
 * Write three-times (technology, features, structure)
 * Layers of abstration
 * Rules apply everywhere
 * Develop your own design rules
 * Learn rules from others
 * Follow the leader
